e product is clothing:\n- make the garment look freshly ironed, clean, smooth, and professionally prepared\n- remove wrinkles, creases, folds, dust, lint, and phone-photo imperfections\n- if it is a vertical outfit, long dress, abaya, jilbab, shirt, coat, robe, or similar hanging garment, display it neatly on a simple elegant hanger\n- keep the full outfit visible from top to bottom\n- do not put it on a person, body, mannequin, or visible face\n- make the hanger realistic and minimal, preferably wood or matte neutral\n- make the garment hang naturally and symmetrically\n\nImprove the image professionally:\n- make the product sharper and cleaner\n- correct exposure and white balance\n- remove dull lighting and phone-camera haze\n- improve fabric detail without changing the garment\n- replace the plain background with a warm elegant studio setting\n- use soft natural window light\n- add subtle shadows for depth\n- create a clean beige/off-white wall and floor\n- optionally add minimal Algerian-inspired decor, such as a ceramic vase, olive branches, brass accent, or subtle geometric pattern\n- keep the scene uncluttered and premium\n- make it suitable for Instagram, Facebook ads, and an online shop product page\n\nComposition:\n- product centered\n- full item visible\n- no cropping\n- enough empty space around the product\n- vertical product photography style\n- realistic commercial photo\n- high-end boutique look\n- natural colors\n- clean marketing asset\n\nStrict restrictions:\nNo visible faces. No people. No body parts. No mannequin. No text. No watermark. No logo added. No fake brand label. No dramatic fantasy background. No excessive redesign. Do not change the product identity."],"color":"#232","bgcolor":"#353"},{"id":67,"type":"CLIPTextEncode","pos":[43.666666014853874,534.0277718670993],"size":[430,88],"flags":{},"order":7,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"clip","name":"clip","type":"CLIP","link":152}],"outputs":[{"localized_name":"CONDITIONING","name":"C